content.rendered: The ultimate “all weather” workboat! This workboat with a perfect price-quality ratio is equipped with a cabin. This allows you to continue working even in rain and strong wind. The cockpit is self-draining and has ample seating and storage space. The Worker 850 is available with either an outboard or an inboard engine, with a choice of diesel or petrol.
